query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating, MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor, MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, kind_type AS kt, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE kt.id = t.kind_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND t.title not like '%picture%' AND n.gender in ('f') AND (n.name like '%n%' OR n.name like '%d%' OR n.name like '%E%') AND (k.keyword like '%war%' OR k.keyword like '%romance%' OR k.keyword like '%secret%' OR k.keyword like '%horror%') AND cct1.kind in ('complete','crew') AND cct2.kind in ('complete+verified','complete') AND mi_idx.info < '2.0' AND chn.name not like '%Marty McFly%' AND chn.name not like '%Doctor Strange%' AND chn.name not like '%Captain Jack Sparrow%' AND chn.name not like '%Luke Skywalker%' AND chn.name not like '%Marty McFly%'
